                " covering a range from 90 deg. to 20 deg. with respect",
                " to the beam direction."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "DECAY"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " From the activity of the 149.0 keV composite",
                "  gamma line, the independent yield of 131-Te-m and",
                "  131-Te-g and thus its high spin fraction at six",
                "  different angles were calculated using the decay-",
                "  growth equation after correcting for precursor",
                "  (131-Sb) contributions."
              ]
            }
